{
  "stem": "1061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I said to myself, maybe we'll just-- they will just march us out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, that wouldn't fit the picture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there has to be some shooting going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then maybe the bombs will fall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whatever it was, I absolutely couldn't imagine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the fact is, I was with my sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We all three lived of us in that unit underneath.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The bombs were falling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They all sent us down, you know, to sit out the air raid, which we did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were glad of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because now they-- the Germans we scared, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So you see, now when we suffered, we at least saw that they have something to worry about, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Although, by that time, you know, if the bomb fell, we never had any idea what happened to mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We, we didn't know about father at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were just the three of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we were together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And if the bombs were to take us, it really would have been fine, in the sense that all the horror that we went through, we certainly could not to go through again.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had no idea if the war is at an end or in the middle or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I, in my-- in my small child's mind was very glad to see that the German women that we served, that they were as scared as, as any of us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to myself, well, maybe they'll now know what it feels like to, to live with fear every second of your life and-- and to anticipate greater horror, which is the only thing that the experience taught us, you know.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
